title: Sitting
projectDate: 2013
description: Images from an ongoing AHRC funded practice based PhD which
  examines the traditional photographic portrait studio and its apparatus as a
  space for the articulation of identity and desire. Through a number of
  different strategies the studio becomes interrogated in an attempt to find a
  visual language adequate to the exploration of its psychic economy and
  coercive discourse.
